leadership-approach|people_process_vision_results|strength_2|2|Commitment with clear conditions|People and Process together can make collaboration easier to sustain. The strength is that trust is supported by clear roles, reliable steps, and standards people can understand.|process|active|leadership-approach::people_process_vision_results::strength_2
leadership-approach|people_process_vision_results|strength_3|3|Range through firmer ownership after Vision|Vision can broaden the first two signals before Results is brought in deliberately. Results adds range when the pattern has already created trust, structure, or direction and now needs a clearer decision. It can turn good leadership intent into ownership, visible movement, and follow-through.|results|active|leadership-approach::people_process_vision_results::strength_3
